data.description: Gorgeous 20.16 acres of land located in the gated Pine Mountain Preserve community off Co Rd 461. Beautiful and quiet country living but close enough to all the conveniences. Located about 2 miles from the Chelsea Publix and 3 miles to Chelsea Walmart. No RR crossings to deal with High speed fiber internet. Fire hydrants. About 1,330 LF of creek runs through the property and serves as the western property line.  Has water year round.About 800 linear feet of water frontage on a beautiful 19 acre lake2.25 +/- acre flat green field. Great deer and turkey population  Existing metal roof pavilion that is approximately 24.5 ft wide x 41 ft long open pavilion with concrete floor. Bathrooms and electrical room is 24.5 ft wide x 15.5 ft long. Existing 8 ft x 12 ft storage building. Several internal roads already cleared. Good mixture of pine and hardwood. Nice building location available near center of the property.
